feedback_text: Battery life is incredible - lasting 14 days on single charge. Huge improvement over V1.
Finally a pet collar that doesn't need constant charging. Very impressed.
Took my dog swimming and the collar worked perfectly. IP68 rating is legit.
GPS tracking is much more accurate than V1. Only minor drift in dense urban areas.
New app interface is beautiful and intuitive. Love the dashboard widgets.
Heart rate monitoring seems accurate. Would like to see sleep tracking improved.
Two weeks without charging - this is a game changer for pet owners.
Submerged in pool for 30 minutes during testing - zero issues.
15 minute charge gives 3 days of battery. Perfect for forgetful owners.
Drop tested from 6 feet onto concrete - not a scratch. Very durable.
